{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p08/qinche_pure_p08_0001.wav", "text": "领替性不错,我没调查你的地址,所以现在在打电话问你。", "duration": 4.668}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0009.wav", "text": "刚上来时还边蹬踏板边哼歌拍照,怎么蹬着蹬着话都不说了。", "duration": 4.668}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p10/qinche_pure_p10_0008.wav", "text": "不是说总觉得有人在暗中盯着你吗你最近还是少用以后为好", "duration": 4.636}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0009.wav", "text": "要是这把剑不太顺手,不如先看看这里最特别的一件东西。", "duration": 4.572}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0046.wav", "text": "人在失去视觉时其他感官会变得更加敏感", "duration": 4.572}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0000.wav", "text": "可能是跟你认识久了待人宽和了不少无用的人词", "duration": 4.572}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0033.wav", "text": "这个过程需要精准把握温度和力度不然很容易出现各种意外", "duration": 4.508}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0019.wav", "text": "况且不来点意外怎么看到你意料之外的表情", "duration": 4.508}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0071.wav", "text": "听说只有小动物才喜欢用拱脑袋的方式来表达自己的想法。", "duration": 4.476}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0010.wav", "text": "他不是胆小,胆小的动物不会露出这种沉着的眼神。", "duration": 4.476}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0043.wav", "text": "它本來也只是一個跟不上時代被淘汰的鍛造師", "duration": 4.444}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0070.wav", "text": "否则我可不敢保证能守住你和秦澈一起当蜗牛这个秘密。", "duration": 4.444}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0054.wav", "text": "大摩很少有意外发生,每一次结果都在意料之中。", "duration": 4.412}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p09/qinche_pure_p09_0010.wav", "text": "形容一个人很不怕死,凭最小的胆子做最胆大的事。", "duration": 4.412}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0049.wav", "text": "毕竟一双能看到我所有另一面的眼睛,就应该像现在这样。", "duration": 4.412}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0044.wav", "text": "夜营时需要经年累月的吸收能量团所以才这么罕见", "duration": 4.316}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0106.wav", "text": "但每一道刻痕都完美符合预期的东西,反而很无趣不是吗?", "duration": 4.284}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0005.wav", "text": "放心,在这里你想怎么处理就怎么处理。", "duration": 4.284}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0015.wav", "text": "现在我好像更理解一条绳子上的蚂蚱是什么感觉了。", "duration": 4.284}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p10/qinche_pure_p10_0011.wav", "text": "但一天听他告八百次状控诉你的罪行也挺有意思。", "duration": 4.284}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0049.wav", "text": "没这么脆弱就算累坏了也能准时出现在你面前", "duration": 4.252}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0029.wav", "text": "要让你这个初学者全程靠人力恐怕明天会起不了床", "duration": 4.22}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0072.wav", "text": "我倒觉得偶尔用动物的方式来表达不算坏方法。", "duration": 4.22}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0057.wav", "text": "说来旅游的这段时间 你好像只在傍晚和夜间安排行程", "duration": 4.22}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0015.wav", "text": "他们是人类攻击最直接的眼神,也是人类最诚实的欲望。", "duration": 4.188}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0023.wav", "text": "要是我去了并且顺利回来,以后就彻底消失在你面前。", "duration": 4.188}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0104.wav", "text": "每一次切割和打磨都在预期之中算不上大麻烦", "duration": 4.156}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0107.wav", "text": "我会很期待那些预期之外的刻痕所带来的连锁反应", "duration": 4.156}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0048.wav", "text": "所有能让你忘掉烦恼和压力的地方我都喜欢", "duration": 4.156}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0006.wav", "text": "还有哪位世面这么热心,每次都把你从生死边缘捡回来。", "duration": 4.124}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0011.wav", "text": "天快黑了你跟着向导先进去我很快就带他跟上", "duration": 4.092}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0020.wav", "text": "应该花了不少心思看来你对和我演戏已经轻车熟路了", "duration": 4.06}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0019.wav", "text": "他我一个人扔下还是我们在这骑马放羊", "duration": 4.06}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0011.wav", "text": "不扑腾怎么把其他船都甩在身后减少几个目击证人", "duration": 4.028}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0063.wav", "text": "我问他们这里的人一般用什么方式向心上人表达感情", "duration": 3.996}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0003.wav", "text": "要做什么不一样的表情才能让那群玩偶不轮流上来踩你的脚?", "duration": 3.996}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0018.wav", "text": "他是让我们也像这里的人一样用果浆在脸上涂花纹", "duration": 3.964}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0021.wav", "text": "看来在你眼里,我所有身份的本质都是强盗。", "duration": 3.964}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0026.wav", "text": "要不是你好奇,这个锻造室大概会永远几回。", "duration": 3.932}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0016.wav", "text": "你去N109去随便抓个人问问谁在我身边有你放送", "duration": 3.9}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p08/qinche_pure_p08_0010.wav", "text": "左一个不行右一个不许你好凶", "duration": 3.868}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0044.wav", "text": "顺手解决几个不长眼的人而已,原来他们就是你的任务。", "duration": 3.868}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0002.wav", "text": "要是子弹用腻了,锻造势力还有更适合你的武器。", "duration": 3.836}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p08/qinche_pure_p08_0004.wav", "text": "还是直接打印一张,贴在你们行动部那层楼的电梯口吧。", "duration": 3.836}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0000.wav", "text": "有些东西存在就是为了让人利用它走捷径", "duration": 3.836}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0045.wav", "text": "毕竟是我们一起种的。", "duration": 3.74}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0047.wav", "text": "你的花车巡游和过山车不是还都没看过玩过吗?", "duration": 3.74}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0032.wav", "text": "速度要快不要让它冷却冷却了就再次加热", "duration": 3.708}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0031.wav", "text": "如果温度不够或材质不好在这一步很容易出现问题", "duration": 3.676}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0058.wav", "text": "他要是长了嘴大概也想问问怎么会发生这种意外", "duration": 3.676}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0025.wav", "text": "你在龙背上转得头晕眼花的时候还能顾得上看夜景", "duration": 3.676}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0010.wav", "text": "一种冷门的兵器全刃最适合贴身搏斗", "duration": 3.612}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0007.wav", "text": "我这个人,向来对任何威胁都不太在意。", "duration": 3.58}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0022.wav", "text": "万一出了什么事,不就没有人打乱你的生活了吗?", "duration": 3.58}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p04/qinche_pure_p04_0000.wav", "text": "要我给你导航,不怕把你导去N109区。", "duration": 3.548}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0031.wav", "text": "这样的烟花能抵消你没看上花车巡演的执念了", "duration": 3.548}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0059.wav", "text": "你刚才磨掉的那一部分也就价值几个暗点而已", "duration": 3.516}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0043.wav", "text": "他长大了不就和周围的树一样要看现在就能看", "duration": 3.516}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p09/qinche_pure_p09_0008.wav", "text": "知道了你在说我很厉害那你的名字呢", "duration": 3.516}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0012.wav", "text": "免得我好心收留小猫却一点也养不熟", "duration": 3.484}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0008.wav", "text": "撒一个谎可是要用一千个谎话去圆的", "duration": 3.452}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0039.wav", "text": "下次想保密的时候,记得把眼圈下的阴影遮一遮。", "duration": 3.452}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0018.wav", "text": "我在你们协会的档案里应该是划分到高级机密吧", "duration": 3.42}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0036.wav", "text": "就当是给床头柜上多天剑衬手的武器不好吗?", "duration": 3.42}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0050.wav", "text": "只是十天不见就养成了爱帮人挠痒的习惯", "duration": 3.388}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0009.wav", "text": "我只是个开水果超市的 还长了一张大众脸", "duration": 3.388}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0002.wav", "text": "不是说心里想什么就讲出来,才是真诚相待吗?", "duration": 3.388}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0008.wav", "text": "你看上别人开的哪艘船了,我们跳上去抢来。", "duration": 3.356}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0082.wav", "text": "这是街头魔头专用的手势,邀请对方来一局的意思。", "duration": 3.324}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0069.wav", "text": "编的时候就在想你戴起来会非常合适", "duration": 3.324}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0003.wav", "text": "毕竟我不是钱,不会所有人都认识我。", "duration": 3.292}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p08/qinche_pure_p08_0005.wav", "text": "那你说个能接受的交接方式,他们已经出发了。", "duration": 3.292}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0051.wav", "text": "需要我帮你给走失的声带贴一张寻物告示吗?", "duration": 3.26}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0003.wav", "text": "这是第一件像样的东西,不过重量稍轻力点。", "duration": 3.228}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0001.wav", "text": "行事守则第一条,保持淡定。", "duration": 3.228}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p10/qinche_pure_p10_0005.wav", "text": "当着他的面色这些还指望他不跟我告状", "duration": 3.228}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0002.wav", "text": "换成你被我故意困在那堆鹅先生哥小姐里,", "duration": 3.228}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0089.wav", "text": "先想想追上他们后打什么手势,再追也不迟。", "duration": 3.196}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0012.wav", "text": "要是累了,受伤了,不想努力了。", "duration": 3.196}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0030.wav", "text": "哦,不是自画像,那现在是呢?", "duration": 3.196}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0033.wav", "text": "就有了十分钟没头了", "duration": 3.196}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0051.wav", "text": "把他放在抛盘上,和你想要的形状来打磨。", "duration": 3.164}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0027.wav", "text": "也许这是我们的最后一面,猎人小姐。", "duration": 3.132}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0012.wav", "text": "怪不得你算个好猎人你的腿在流血", "duration": 3.132}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0001.wav", "text": "是啊不说别人怎么会知道", "duration": 3.132}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p08/qinche_pure_p08_0009.wav", "text": "伪造身份参与以朝交易的手法良民", "duration": 3.132}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0006.wav", "text": "只不过刚才被关心了一下,现在已经好多了。", "duration": 3.1}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0030.wav", "text": "我怎么不知道自己什么时候有的这种爱好。", "duration": 3.1}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0110.wav", "text": "花瓣帶著你一起出現在了龍的夢裡", "duration": 3.068}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0019.wav", "text": "想得很美但别忘了我也有武器", "duration": 3.068}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0075.wav", "text": "你不覺得應該把煙花作為這場約會的結尾嗎", "duration": 3.036}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0005.wav", "text": "这是因为这一次对我来说并不是陷阱", "duration": 3.004}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0022.wav", "text": "刚才已经跟你预告过了是你太过轻敌", "duration": 3.004}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p09/qinche_pure_p09_0004.wav", "text": "这个流浪体怎么都解决不了真是太清澈了", "duration": 3.004}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0011.wav", "text": "喜欢收藏一些能弄出声响的小玩意儿", "duration": 2.972}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0046.wav", "text": "要是想看到时候我们可以再来旅游一次", "duration": 2.972}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0003.wav", "text": "很多人都说我是大众脸经常被人搓", "duration": 2.94}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0028.wav", "text": "就用你的枪送他一个难忘的道理。", "duration": 2.908}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0025.wav", "text": "凌空公园的红叶还有美食街的烤板栗", "duration": 2.908}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0028.wav", "text": "你的背就要把身后那盆无辜的紫杨花推下去了", "duration": 2.908}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0036.wav", "text": "我看千锤百炼的好像不是他,而是你。", "duration": 2.876}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0013.wav", "text": "刚才就看你想上手,现在不需要顾忌了。", "duration": 2.876}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0038.wav", "text": "这个时间就出现我猜你昨晚也没睡", "duration": 2.876}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0109.wav", "text": "昨晚睡着的时候我做了个梦", "duration": 2.844}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0032.wav", "text": "说好了彻底消失 就不能藕断丝连", "duration": 2.844}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0005.wav", "text": "我现在是多么好脾气的珍惜和爱护着你", "duration": 2.844}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0038.wav", "text": "认识我这么久了你现在才注意到", "duration": 2.844}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0044.wav", "text": "我们一起种的树确实和别的树不一样", "duration": 2.844}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0037.wav", "text": "至少比在枕头下放枪安全多了", "duration": 2.844}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0020.wav", "text": "他的凶名是战场上杀出来的", "duration": 2.812}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0094.wav", "text": "看来过了这么多年露台也变成了一块牌子", "duration": 2.812}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0034.wav", "text": "你还是第一个敢对我说不准的人。", "duration": 2.812}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0015.wav", "text": "手机还有电吧,不来留下我的罪证吗?", "duration": 2.812}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0037.wav", "text": "有没有人跟你说过你还挺有创意的", "duration": 2.78}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p10/qinche_pure_p10_0002.wav", "text": "要是能把机械乌鸦养死那算你本事", "duration": 2.78}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0084.wav", "text": "和这种小鬼做仇家 会拉低我的档次", "duration": 2.748}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0095.wav", "text": "现在只能和这块牌子拍张照证明来过了", "duration": 2.748}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0015.wav", "text": "舍夫尼克舍夫尼克", "duration": 2.748}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0027.wav", "text": "开车的时候看你喜欢多送你几个", "duration": 2.748}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0000.wav", "text": "好看吗打算看到什么时候", "duration": 2.716}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0079.wav", "text": "既然不想浪费时间就让自己有好心情", "duration": 2.716}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0017.wav", "text": "受伤的人睡了可能会醒不过来", "duration": 2.716}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0026.wav", "text": "只要是人就有打败他的办法", "duration": 2.716}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0036.wav", "text": "就装在这里也当是我们来过的证明", "duration": 2.716}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0007.wav", "text": "不想说的话用行动表示也可以", "duration": 2.684}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0016.wav", "text": "原来得寸进尺不是我一个人的专利。", "duration": 2.684}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0026.wav", "text": "画了什么这么喜欢,笑得眉飞色舞的。", "duration": 2.684}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0105.wav", "text": "不在掌控中的切割我的确不喜欢", "duration": 2.652}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0045.wav", "text": "你的封口费还真是别出新词", "duration": 2.652}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0042.wav", "text": "不给一件回礼都说不过去了", "duration": 2.62}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0010.wav", "text": "别人可能是被我的和蔼可亲吸引了吧,", "duration": 2.62}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0086.wav", "text": "你已经下班了别再满脑子打打杀杀", "duration": 2.588}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0020.wav", "text": "谁在谁脸上画还不一定呢", "duration": 2.556}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0080.wav", "text": "再过你又不止一次心情已经转换好了", "duration": 2.524}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0005.wav", "text": "想象你面前是手持盾牌的士兵", "duration": 2.492}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0099.wav", "text": "唱歌的感觉很真实 不像幻觉", "duration": 2.492}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0022.wav", "text": "想跟我回案点,就直说。", "duration": 2.492}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0004.wav", "text": "软件不是用来劈卡,而是刺激。", "duration": 2.46}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0066.wav", "text": "毕竟我现在能信任的人可不多", "duration": 2.46}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0014.wav", "text": "猎人小姐总是能带给人新体验,", "duration": 2.46}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0002.wav", "text": "偶尔会有些没脑子的家伙向我挑衅", "duration": 2.46}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0066.wav", "text": "时间有限 编得有点粗糙就是", "duration": 2.46}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p09/qinche_pure_p09_0003.wav", "text": "听你这句意,是完蛋了的意思啊?", "duration": 2.46}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p10/qinche_pure_p10_0000.wav", "text": "十几个你的未接来电有事", "duration": 2.46}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0014.wav", "text": "巧了,我最喜欢顶风作案。", "duration": 2.46}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0010.wav", "text": "等以后想起来了再一并找你", "duration": 2.428}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p04/qinche_pure_p04_0002.wav", "text": "喜欢这么勤彻的导航吗?", "duration": 2.428}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0022.wav", "text": "学会的东西不会这么快忘记。", "duration": 2.428}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0000.wav", "text": "能让我搭个便车吗这位小姐", "duration": 2.428}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0005.wav", "text": "我也觉得有点冷", "duration": 2.428}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0101.wav", "text": "顺便让他们看看我新搜罗来的", "duration": 2.396}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0015.wav", "text": "感动完自己开始感动我了", "duration": 2.396}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0001.wav", "text": "不鲜艳一点怎么吸引你的视线?", "duration": 2.396}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0042.wav", "text": "看这样子,少说也要十几年吧。", "duration": 2.396}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0049.wav", "text": "搞什么,晚会才刚刚开始。", "duration": 2.396}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p09/qinche_pure_p09_0005.wav", "text": "原来你一直想把我当成流浪体解决", "duration": 2.396}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p09/qinche_pure_p09_0002.wav", "text": "两个姓薛的,是被你传染的吧?", "duration": 2.364}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p10/qinche_pure_p10_0009.wav", "text": "有什么事就叫梅菲斯特帮你去做", "duration": 2.364}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p10/qinche_pure_p10_0010.wav", "text": "突然真以为我无聊到送她去监视你", "duration": 2.364}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0026.wav", "text": "国王的晚宴,要赴约吗?", "duration": 2.364}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0081.wav", "text": "接上我們的車,終點跨了土莊。", "duration": 2.332}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0016.wav", "text": "我说不可以,你就不睡了。", "duration": 2.332}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0052.wav", "text": "哦 原来是惩罚升级了", "duration": 2.332}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0022.wav", "text": "那你今天打算继续做我的供饭", "duration": 2.332}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0038.wav", "text": "现在算是完成了最重要的第一阶段", "duration": 2.3}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0037.wav", "text": "这才刚刚开始还能坚持", "duration": 2.268}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0001.wav", "text": "还没想好见到我之后的开场白吗", "duration": 2.268}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0011.wav", "text": "还以为只有猫才会对红点感兴趣", "duration": 2.236}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0007.wav", "text": "我們應該互相向對方學習", "duration": 2.236}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0008.wav", "text": "你不觉得在这个完全陌生的地方", "duration": 2.236}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0017.wav", "text": "嗯只是因为游乐园", "duration": 2.236}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0028.wav", "text": "不用在这里像站岗一样不累吗", "duration": 2.204}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0007.wav", "text": "开始发威了 万寿之王", "duration": 2.204}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0068.wav", "text": "再低一点头冠就要掉了", "duration": 2.204}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0006.wav", "text": "这个理由比防晒更容易让人接受", "duration": 2.204}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0012.wav", "text": "你知不知道自己上了艘什么样的船", "duration": 2.204}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0017.wav", "text": "有些经典的短刀是格斗的王者,", "duration": 2.172}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0055.wav", "text": "你賦予她什麼樣的力度和方向", "duration": 2.172}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0004.wav", "text": "你人真好,大慈善家。", "duration": 2.172}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p09/qinche_pure_p09_0006.wav", "text": "比如再造个剧我听听", "duration": 2.172}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0087.wav", "text": "你挑对手的标准就是眼光一致", "duration": 2.108}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0055.wav", "text": "要惩罚我就别迁怒棉花糖了", "duration": 2.108}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p08/qinche_pure_p08_0006.wav", "text": "记得找个收件时不用物品扫描的地方", "duration": 2.108}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p08/qinche_pure_p08_0012.wav", "text": "下次见面是亲自带给你。", "duration": 2.099375}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0015.wav", "text": "真是要少很多乐趣了", "duration": 2.0780416666666666}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0093.wav", "text": "電影《日不落之城》曾拍攝地", "duration": 2.044}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0046.wav", "text": "那就再多去几趟买回了", "duration": 2.044}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0006.wav", "text": "那要是被你的同事们发现了,", "duration": 2.012}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0003.wav", "text": "倒是第一次知道气球还需要溜", "duration": 2.012}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p08/qinche_pure_p08_0003.wav", "text": "效率的确低下", "duration": 2.012}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p10/qinche_pure_p10_0012.wav", "text": "你对这么可爱的小动物下得去手", "duration": 2.012}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0012.wav", "text": "记得回去的路吗小家伙", "duration": 1.98}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0054.wav", "text": "你的棉花糖看起来很火热", "duration": 1.98}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0067.wav", "text": "还满意吗心伤人", "duration": 1.98}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p10/qinche_pure_p10_0015.wav", "text": "有一天竟然要给你和鸟做调停", "duration": 1.98}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0085.wav", "text": "刚才那些都是赢家的嘲讽手势", "duration": 1.948}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p04/qinche_pure_p04_0003.wav", "text": "你的答案我知道了。", "duration": 1.9180416666666666}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0021.wav", "text": "走吧 我送你回家", "duration": 1.916}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0016.wav", "text": "你那些只在我面前露出的样子", "duration": 1.916}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0028.wav", "text": "画在脸上省得举手去溜", "duration": 1.916}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0071.wav", "text": "在我脸上画了颗心之后", "duration": 1.916}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p10/qinche_pure_p10_0013.wav", "text": "怎么和一只鸟的关系都处不好", "duration": 1.916}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0052.wav", "text": "放到桌上 这样会轻松点", "duration": 1.884}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0067.wav", "text": "做的事情 薛民薛也会解决", "duration": 1.884}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0023.wav", "text": "还是扮演一下被我劫掠的对象。", "duration": 1.884}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0029.wav", "text": "也可以让任何地方适应我。", "duration": 1.852}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0035.wav", "text": "那就把他们留在最合适的地方。", "duration": 1.852}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0008.wav", "text": "有一种心跳加速的感觉", "duration": 1.82}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0016.wav", "text": "可惜我们之间的那条绳子", "duration": 1.788}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0019.wav", "text": "你能知道这个级别的信息", "duration": 1.788}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p10/qinche_pure_p10_0001.wav", "text": "他住够了会自己飞回来", "duration": 1.788}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0073.wav", "text": "这俩姓薛的至少还记得正是", "duration": 1.756}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0006.wav", "text": "这些个眼神足够了", "duration": 1.756}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0015.wav", "text": "可是有狩猎巫妖的胆量呢", "duration": 1.756}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0000.wav", "text": "那我多说几遍让你能记得。", "duration": 1.756}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0023.wav", "text": "只是因为想见对方就见面", "duration": 1.756}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0005.wav", "text": "能跑到我都找不到的地方去", "duration": 1.756}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0007.wav", "text": "还记得教过你的拳击动作吗", "duration": 1.724}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0021.wav", "text": "可你好像已经逐渐习惯了。", "duration": 1.724}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0058.wav", "text": "天气这么好却晒不了太阳", "duration": 1.724}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0073.wav", "text": "不能让你从我身边离开了", "duration": 1.724}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p09/qinche_pure_p09_0011.wav", "text": "弄死也有了狡辩", "duration": 1.724}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0012.wav", "text": "不過倒也不用這麼尊師重道,", "duration": 1.692}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0002.wav", "text": "小本买卖", "duration": 1.692}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0003.wav", "text": "当时没有一个像你这样", "duration": 1.692}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0024.wav", "text": "那我要是想多看一会儿呢?", "duration": 1.692}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0025.wav", "text": "今天的事", "duration": 1.692}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0047.wav", "text": "十几年以后", "duration": 1.692}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0077.wav", "text": "如果有一天想換個地方生活", "duration": 1.66}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0014.wav", "text": "不知道太多会被杀掉", "duration": 1.66}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0009.wav", "text": "能不能让我带她四处走走", "duration": 1.66}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0041.wav", "text": "小心撞树上了", "duration": 1.66}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0029.wav", "text": "你也没少做让我担心的事", "duration": 1.66}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0035.wav", "text": "钱都印出来,不用选了。", "duration": 1.66}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0041.wav", "text": "误证也有了,", "duration": 1.66}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0027.wav", "text": "幸好这台老古董还能开机", "duration": 1.628}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0056.wav", "text": "就会留下什么样的刻痕", "duration": 1.628}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0000.wav", "text": "记住保持好你的风氛", "duration": 1.628}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0009.wav", "text": "臣反而没有那么多顾虑吗", "duration": 1.628}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0002.wav", "text": "你在我身边越来越放松了", "duration": 1.628}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0032.wav", "text": "也差不多要毁容了", "duration": 1.628}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0001.wav", "text": "不是想看我之前鍛造的武器", "duration": 1.596}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0097.wav", "text": "不影响我打视频啃猫。", "duration": 1.596}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0031.wav", "text": "毕竟我是愿赌服输的人", "duration": 1.596}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0037.wav", "text": "不算我打乱你的生活了吧", "duration": 1.596}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0001.wav", "text": "你真的不会让人觉得无聊", "duration": 1.596}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0011.wav", "text": "下次善用你的通讯设备。", "duration": 1.596}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0040.wav", "text": "想起我的哪些样子了", "duration": 1.596}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0062.wav", "text": "不是好奇我刚才在聊什么吗", "duration": 1.596}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0064.wav", "text": "照当地的习俗做了这个", "duration": 1.596}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0065.wav", "text": "跟你去拿棉花糖的时候编的", "duration": 1.596}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p08/qinche_pure_p08_0008.wav", "text": "所以我建议你亲自接受。", "duration": 1.596}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0057.wav", "text": "很别致的不规则切割", "duration": 1.564}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0018.wav", "text": "连这首曲子都想起来了。", "duration": 1.564}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0031.wav", "text": "我的杰作", "duration": 1.564}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0009.wav", "text": "我偶尔会有些心神不宁", "duration": 1.564}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0034.wav", "text": "反正在N109活不了", "duration": 1.564}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0030.wav", "text": "不过现在多了一个前提", "duration": 1.532}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0002.wav", "text": "还以为你其实不想见到我。", "duration": 1.532}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0061.wav", "text": "你不是好奇我刚才在聊什么吗", "duration": 1.532}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0013.wav", "text": "还要被他挑剔笑得不好", "duration": 1.5}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0001.wav", "text": "那就恭敬不如从命了。", "duration": 1.5}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0013.wav", "text": "也可以直接逃来我身边", "duration": 1.5}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0092.wav", "text": "纯粹的只有你和我", "duration": 1.468}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0100.wav", "text": "情人品酒的普通宴會", "duration": 1.468}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0004.wav", "text": "老大不能说不行", "duration": 1.468}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0013.wav", "text": "我还是第一次和人合唱", "duration": 1.468}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0035.wav", "text": "你的枪这次帮了我大忙", "duration": 1.468}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p09/qinche_pure_p09_0007.wav", "text": "你倒很会给自己开脱", "duration": 1.468}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0042.wav", "text": "至于让你睡不好的人", "duration": 1.468}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0008.wav", "text": "不能只依靠手臂的力量", "duration": 1.436}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0039.wav", "text": "他很快就會脫胎換骨", "duration": 1.436}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0045.wav", "text": "攜帶我過去的寶石", "duration": 1.436}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0009.wav", "text": "每次我都笑得很和善", "duration": 1.436}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0024.wav", "text": "不会再来打乱你的生活", "duration": 1.436}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0006.wav", "text": "他的行为好像更真诚", "duration": 1.436}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0007.wav", "text": "上船吧海盗小姐", "duration": 1.436}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0010.wav", "text": "才满一点", "duration": 1.436}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0027.wav", "text": "那就敬你的宽宏大量", "duration": 1.436}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0014.wav", "text": "生兵器很有趣不是吗", "duration": 1.404}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0025.wav", "text": "要是我去了没回来", "duration": 1.404}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0030.wav", "text": "现在算你自己违约了", "duration": 1.404}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0006.wav", "text": "我怎么看你还挺享受的", "duration": 1.404}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0028.wav", "text": "我可以适应任何地方", "duration": 1.404}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0004.wav", "text": "你的本事涨进了不少", "duration": 1.404}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0007.wav", "text": "可不由肇事者说了算", "duration": 1.404}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0008.wav", "text": "跳练的应该不是胆子,", "duration": 1.404}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0048.wav", "text": "你不觉得我们会分开", "duration": 1.404}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0072.wav", "text": "竟然回应了我的礼物", "duration": 1.404}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0009.wav", "text": "你欠我的人情还少吗", "duration": 1.372}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0013.wav", "text": "我们耐心慢慢等", "duration": 1.372}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0031.wav", "text": "就这么出去玩刚刚好。", "duration": 1.372}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0005.wav", "text": "还是担心被我牵连", "duration": 1.34}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0008.wav", "text": "你不在的这段时间", "duration": 1.308}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0023.wav", "text": "这么光明正大耍赖", "duration": 1.308}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0050.wav", "text": "我们刚才在聊", "duration": 1.308}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0018.wav", "text": "獵刀為荒野而生", "duration": 1.276}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0053.wav", "text": "不過很快就沒什麼意思了", "duration": 1.276}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0011.wav", "text": "不披萨什的样子", "duration": 1.244}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0014.wav", "text": "一向说话算数", "duration": 1.244}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0070.wav", "text": "又想在我脸上画什么", "duration": 1.244}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p10/qinche_pure_p10_0003.wav", "text": "那不是正合你意吗", "duration": 1.244}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0007.wav", "text": "你会选择站哪一边", "duration": 1.212}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0026.wav", "text": "你也能如愿以偿", "duration": 1.212}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0036.wav", "text": "你自己不好想我", "duration": 1.212}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0004.wav", "text": "你也应该知道了吧", "duration": 1.212}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0010.wav", "text": "你拼尽全力的样子。", "duration": 1.212}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0013.wav", "text": "信任的人看到", "duration": 1.212}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0018.wav", "text": "要是我真輸了", "duration": 1.212}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0000.wav", "text": "来了又躲在一边", "duration": 1.212}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0014.wav", "text": "否则这凌空式", "duration": 1.212}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0004.wav", "text": "太小看我的水平了", "duration": 1.212}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0033.wav", "text": "我倒是也准备了一个", "duration": 1.212}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0004.wav", "text": "你是在担心我", "duration": 1.18}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0017.wav", "text": "好像是剪不断的。", "duration": 1.18}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0008.wav", "text": "不要滥用暴力", "duration": 1.18}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0024.wav", "text": "最重要的东西", "duration": 1.18}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0017.wav", "text": "不需要让别人见到", "duration": 1.18}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0059.wav", "text": "弄你及我好几条了", "duration": 1.18}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0060.wav", "text": "是这样更适合你", "duration": 1.18}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0024.wav", "text": "再晚点人会更少", "duration": 1.18}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0029.wav", "text": "我们不应该再见面", "duration": 1.148}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0014.wav", "text": "你很会自我感动", "duration": 1.148}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0027.wav", "text": "喜欢你的头发", "duration": 1.148}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0015.wav", "text": "你自己没察觉到吗", "duration": 1.148}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p09/qinche_pure_p09_0001.wav", "text": "人撤了是什么意思啊", "duration": 1.148}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p09/qinche_pure_p09_0009.wav", "text": "解释一下你的名字", "duration": 1.148}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0063.wav", "text": "什么都有可能发生", "duration": 1.116}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0011.wav", "text": "想得到我的真诚", "duration": 1.116}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0012.wav", "text": "能让最亲密", "duration": 1.116}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0043.wav", "text": "求我一个就够了。", "duration": 1.116}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0004.wav", "text": "是我的端端", "duration": 1.084}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p06/qinche_pure_p06_0003.wav", "text": "倒是活蹦乱跳", "duration": 1.084}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0001.wav", "text": "忽然你释放一下", "duration": 1.084}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0103.wav", "text": "就像打磨寶石", "duration": 1.052}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p01/qinche_pure_p01_0010.wav", "text": "皮笑肉不笑就够了", "duration": 1.052}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0033.wav", "text": "原来只是玩笑。", "duration": 1.052}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0020.wav", "text": "在越南忘记", "duration": 1.052}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0017.wav", "text": "干杯是会醉的。", "duration": 1.052}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0034.wav", "text": "有什么区别吗?", "duration": 1.052}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0050.wav", "text": "照片拍得挺不错", "duration": 1.052}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_02/qinche_02_0078.wav", "text": "不是说再兜一圈吗", "duration": 1.02}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p02/qinche_pure_p02_0000.wav", "text": "过命的朋友", "duration": 1.02}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p03/qinche_pure_p03_0019.wav", "text": "飘得越深", "duration": 1.02}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0003.wav", "text": "真诚相待", "duration": 1.02}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0020.wav", "text": "你有心上人了", "duration": 1.02}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p05/qinche_pure_p05_0021.wav", "text": "如果不是故意", "duration": 1.02}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p07/qinche_pure_p07_0039.wav", "text": "这个表情", "duration": 1.02}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_pure_p11/qinche_pure_p11_0018.wav", "text": "我不讨厌意外", "duration": 1.02}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0000.wav", "text": "有了什么麻烦事", "duration": 1.212}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0001.wav", "text": "发送的应该是别人", "duration": 1.212}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0002.wav", "text": "我求你,你可以帮我解决麻烦。", "duration": 2.492}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0003.wav", "text": "我好像没说需要帮助", "duration": 1.34}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0004.wav", "text": "什么麻烦是要把我摁在床上解决的", "duration": 2.268}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0005.wav", "text": "不求也得求", "duration": 1.02}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0006.wav", "text": "要我开口求人", "duration": 1.404}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0007.wav", "text": "有什么不平常的方法", "duration": 1.564}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0008.wav", "text": "进攻又很强烈", "duration": 1.372}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0009.wav", "text": "就开始犹犹豫豫", "duration": 1.372}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0010.wav", "text": "就专心忙一件事", "duration": 1.5}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0011.wav", "text": "想听我的评价", "duration": 1.276}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0012.wav", "text": "张嘴就气人", "duration": 1.084}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0013.wav", "text": "不能算得上是开胃菜", "duration": 1.564}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0014.wav", "text": "还微风凛凛地压着我", "duration": 1.5}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0015.wav", "text": "现在就开始后缩了", "duration": 1.148}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0016.wav", "text": "不是说想听我求饶吗", "duration": 1.372}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0017.wav", "text": "要是有什么仇也可以现在报复回来", "duration": 2.716}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0018.wav", "text": "我也有很多有趣的做法", "duration": 1.692}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0019.wav", "text": "要一一尝试", "duration": 1.116}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0020.wav", "text": "检查我的伤", "duration": 1.244}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0021.wav", "text": "都是别人的血", "duration": 1.148}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0022.wav", "text": "如果你不信的话", "duration": 1.084}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0023.wav", "text": "下次要检查,早点说。", "duration": 1.916}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0024.wav", "text": "检查伤口的手法吗", "duration": 1.18}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0025.wav", "text": "总没见识过", "duration": 1.02}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0026.wav", "text": "今晚上我多见识一遍", "duration": 1.34}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0027.wav", "text": "今天都听你的", "duration": 1.052}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0028.wav", "text": "想要我的尾巴", "duration": 1.02}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0029.wav", "text": "狡猾的小猎人", "duration": 1.276}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0030.wav", "text": "有很多种用法", "duration": 1.34}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0031.wav", "text": "这次下手的地方倒是别出心裁", "duration": 2.588}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0032.wav", "text": "但你没说不可以继续用EVO", "duration": 1.916}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0033.wav", "text": "今天都听你的", "duration": 1.02}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0034.wav", "text": "现在有理由正当防卫了吧", "duration": 1.756}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0035.wav", "text": "这么好的景色,应该足够主行。", "duration": 2.876}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0036.wav", "text": "会让我欲望的缺口越来越大", "duration": 1.948}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_01/qinche_01_0037.wav", "text": "这种忠于欲望的样子", "duration": 1.788}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p01/qinche_call_p01_0000.wav", "text": "过半个小时,薛明轩也会给你送个礼物过去,建议你亲自签收。", "duration": 4.764}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p01/qinche_call_p01_0001.wav", "text": "警惕性不错,我没调查你的地址,所以现在在打电话问你。", "duration": 4.732}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p01/qinche_call_p01_0002.wav", "text": "可以那待会儿只好辛苦他们在猎人协会的终端里多播放几次失误招领了", "duration": 6.94}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p01/qinche_call_p01_0003.wav", "text": "效率的确低下", "duration": 1.884}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p01/qinche_call_p01_0004.wav", "text": "还是直接打印一张,贴在你们行动部那层楼的电梯口吧。", "duration": 3.868}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p01/qinche_call_p01_0005.wav", "text": "那你说个能接受的交接方式,他们已经出发了。", "duration": 3.292}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p01/qinche_call_p01_0006.wav", "text": "记得找个收件时不用物品扫描的地方", "duration": 2.044}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p01/qinche_call_p01_0007.wav", "text": "一把枪你现在用的枪没那么顺手这两天组装了一把新的专门针对流浪体非常", "duration": 7.804}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p01/qinche_call_p01_0008.wav", "text": "所以我建议你亲自接受。", "duration": 1.628}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p01/qinche_call_p01_0009.wav", "text": "伪造身份参与以朝交易的手法良民", "duration": 3.1}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p01/qinche_call_p01_0010.wav", "text": "左一个不行右一个不许你好凶啊", "duration": 3.868}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p01/qinche_call_p01_0011.wav", "text": "好吧林空试试你的地盘你做主有事给我打电话", "duration": 5.02}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p01/qinche_call_p01_0012.wav", "text": "下次见面是亲自带给你", "duration": 1.4329166666666666}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p02/qinche_call_p02_0000.wav", "text": "是秦撤了秦撤了的秦撤了是什么意思", "duration": 5.66}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p02/qinche_call_p02_0001.wav", "text": "两个姓薛的,是被你传染的吧?", "duration": 2.396}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p02/qinche_call_p02_0002.wav", "text": "听你这句意是完蛋了的意思啊?", "duration": 2.428}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p02/qinche_call_p02_0003.wav", "text": "这个流浪体怎么都解决不了真是太前车了", "duration": 3.004}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p02/qinche_call_p02_0004.wav", "text": "原来你一直想把我当成流浪体解决", "duration": 2.396}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p02/qinche_call_p02_0005.wav", "text": "比如再造个剧我听听", "duration": 2.172}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p02/qinche_call_p02_0006.wav", "text": "你倒很会给自己开脱", "duration": 1.5}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p02/qinche_call_p02_0007.wav", "text": "知道了你在说我很厉害那你的名字呢", "duration": 3.58}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p02/qinche_call_p02_0008.wav", "text": "解释一下你的名字", "duration": 1.148}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p02/qinche_call_p02_0009.wav", "text": "形容一个人很不怕死,凭最小的胆子做最胆大的事。", "duration": 4.444}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p02/qinche_call_p02_0010.wav", "text": "弄死也有了狡辩", "duration": 1.724}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p02/qinche_call_p02_0011.wav", "text": "还有名词的解释只带一种爪子锋利又养不熟的猫也可以特指一个十分可恶又让人不忍心下手的人", "duration": 10.880375}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0000.wav", "text": "几个你的未接来电有事", "duration": 2.236}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0001.wav", "text": "他住够了会自己飞回来", "duration": 1.788}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0002.wav", "text": "要是能把机械乌鸦养死那算你本事", "duration": 2.812}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0003.wav", "text": "那不是正合你意吗", "duration": 1.244}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0004.wav", "text": "你今天一直在搜N109区的乌鸦,如何关闭机械鸟的电源,尝试了喂鸭喝水敲鸭脑袋宝石溜鸭,这些我都知道。", "duration": 11.452}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0005.wav", "text": "当着他的面色这些还指望他不跟我告状", "duration": 3.196}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0006.wav", "text": "梅菲斯特用途广泛能定位敌人还能察觉到异常信号你会用得上的", "duration": 5.34}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0007.wav", "text": "别妄自菲薄你比你想象中有用的多这几天他都会跟着你出门", "duration": 5.34}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0008.wav", "text": "不是说总觉得有人在暗中盯着你吗你最近还是少用一步为好", "duration": 4.7}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0009.wav", "text": "有什么事就叫梅菲斯特帮你去做", "duration": 2.364}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0010.wav", "text": "忽然真以为我无聊到送她去监视你", "duration": 2.332}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0011.wav", "text": "但一天听他告八百次状控诉你的罪行,也挺有意思。", "duration": 4.284}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0012.wav", "text": "你对这么可爱的小动物下得去手", "duration": 2.012}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0013.wav", "text": "怎么和一只鸟的关系都处不好", "duration": 1.884}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p03/qinche_call_p03_0014.wav", "text": "刚传回来的信号他在告状算了我把它撤回来真没想到有一天竟然要给你和鸟做调停", "duration": 9.122333333333334}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0000.wav", "text": "盯着手机屏幕看了这么久才接才犹豫什么", "duration": 3.26}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0001.wav", "text": "来这里办点私事", "duration": 1.116}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0002.wav", "text": "怕我被抓住", "duration": 2.62}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0003.wav", "text": "挺好还我个小毛", "duration": 1.692}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0004.wav", "text": "我不走过来,难道一头朝你撞过来?", "duration": 2.268}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0005.wav", "text": "我身后跟的也是我的同事", "duration": 1.756}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0006.wav", "text": "你站在走廊口我要进那条走廊里路就这么宽要么你让让", "duration": 5.34}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0007.wav", "text": "你紧张得眼睛都要掉出来了", "duration": 1.82}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0008.wav", "text": "你有没有听过一个词叫欲盖弥彰回避的这么刻意还和我保持距离", "duration": 5.756}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0009.wav", "text": "只会让别人以为我们真的有什么。", "duration": 1.788}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0010.wav", "text": "摸摸口袋给你塞了个小东西", "duration": 2.236}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0011.wav", "text": "我的车钥匙", "duration": 1.244}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0012.wav", "text": "既然你等会儿没事,不如帮我个小忙,我去十五楼和你们协会高层谈点事,万一谈崩了,等你把车发动好,我正好下来,接应好我,凌空市的路况你比我熟。", "duration": 13.276}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0013.wav", "text": "如果真落在你手里就当给你送夜去了", "duration": 2.812}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p04/qinche_call_p04_0014.wav", "text": "没有的话就当凌空一日游别回家睡觉了晚上和我出去开车兜风到地方了先挂了去车里等我一会儿见", "duration": 11.055083333333334}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p05/qinche_call_p05_0000.wav", "text": "你社交账号里点了在看的那篇文章是《极赞领取大佬同款气场修炼秘籍》,教会你如何用一个眼神让对手腿软。", "duration": 10.524}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p05/qinche_call_p05_0001.wav", "text": "从这个秘籍你能学到什么", "duration": 1.532}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p05/qinche_call_p05_0002.wav", "text": "我确实谈不上善良,但戴墨镜是为了避光,嘴角不必上扬这条,我是保留意见,最重要的是,我从来不滥用暴力,不随便给人一枪。", "duration": 12.124}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p05/qinche_call_p05_0003.wav", "text": "比你这个不靠谱的秘籍好一点", "duration": 1.916}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p05/qinche_call_p05_0004.wav", "text": "你在我面前不是张牙舞爪无所畏惧那些参会的人难道比我可怕", "duration": 4.636}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p05/qinche_call_p05_0005.wav", "text": "问题解决了", "duration": 1.532}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p05/qinche_call_p05_0006.wav", "text": "上位者参加晚宴往往是在享受,你只需要端着酒杯慢慢喝,自然有人上来打话。", "duration": 6.396}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p05/qinche_call_p05_0007.wav", "text": "渐编的N109去大佬气场修炼秘籍", "duration": 2.748}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p05/qinche_call_p05_0008.wav", "text": "本来就是宴会的具体时间", "duration": 2.364}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p05/qinche_call_p05_0009.wav", "text": "你打算直接去参加晚宴吗不如", "duration": 2.684}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p05/qinche_call_p05_0010.wav", "text": "下周二还有一段时间你可以先来找我演习看网传秘籍那些歪门邪道只会让你误入歧途来N109区亲自体验过才知道", "duration": 11.457791666666667}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p06/qinche_call_p06_0000.wav", "text": "如果不是听出你的声音,还以为这是诈骗电话的开场白。", "duration": 4.156}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p06/qinche_call_p06_0001.wav", "text": "什么事 说吧", "duration": 1.532}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p06/qinche_call_p06_0002.wav", "text": "认真的吗让我帮你抽你怎么没有先测一下我的运气指数有多少", "duration": 5.66}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p06/qinche_call_p06_0003.wav", "text": "你又怎么确定测出这个61没有花光我今天的好运,劝你还是找别人吧。", "duration": 5.532}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p06/qinche_call_p06_0004.wav", "text": "我的理财方式不包括瓜瓜乐,你身边就没有其他人测出比61大的数字了。", "duration": 5.532}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p06/qinche_call_p06_0005.wav", "text": "如果结果不好你可别后悔", "duration": 2.268}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p06/qinche_call_p06_0006.wav", "text": "定运与否不好说,你的乐观指数一定比一般人高,要怎么帮你?", "duration": 5.34}
{"audio_filepath": "/home/ubuntu/yunlin/TTS/data/segments/qinche_call_p06/qinche_call_p06_0007.wav", "text": "今天的运气确实还算不错", "duration": 1.9126666666666667}
